%h1 ChirpyBox
%h2 A Suggestion Box in the Cloud
%p.margin-bottom
  We're still hammering together our first few ChirpyBoxes. Want us to let you know when we're ready to make one for you?
.display-table
= form_for(@invite) do |f|
  .table-row
    .table-cell.table-cell-field
      = f.text_field :email, placeholder:"your@email.com", type:"email", class:"signup-text-field"
    .table-cell.table-cell-submit
      = f.submit 'Let me know!', class:"submit-button"
  - if notice
    .table-row
      .table-cell
        %p.error = notice